text: Joglekar is an Indian name. It may refer to: *Archana Joglekar, Indian actress. *Gautam Joglekar, Indian actor. *Manoj Joglekar, Indian cricketer. *Padmaja Phenany Joglekar, Hindustani Classical singer *Vasant Joglekar, Indian film director. Category:Indian masculine given names
title: Joglekar
